window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Never sell your soul to the Demon King....</p> <p>Too late. </p> <p>In an effort to save all that I love, I have to finish the job that Nyfain started....And ruin myself.</p> <p>I've made a trade with the most cunning creature alive. Me for them. The dungeons will be my new home. </p> <p>Dolion's destruction will be my new goal.</p> <p>I just have to get out of here, and back to my golden dragon. Preferably alive.</p>"; 
